%!PS

%	This example appears in section "More About Bezier Curves"
%	in Chapter 7 - "Arcs and Curves".
%

/inch { 72 mul } def			%  define inch procedure
4.25 inch 5.5 inch			%  center of circle
4 inch					%  radius of circle
0 90 arc				%  complete 360 degree arc
0.125 inch setlinewidth			%  fat line width
stroke					%  paint path
showpage				%  display page
